name: FlashbangFeed
0:
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
”Alexa, play my Flash Briefing”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des: When you ask for your flash briefing this will provide CSGO news with it! Get updates on your favorite teams, tournaments, rule changes, and roster updates. This provides a great way to keep up with the latest in CSGO easily.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
